{"tid":2444204,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門好","createTime":"2021-03-12T14:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T14:52:55.000Z","uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e902871282391a32f1e1e09050cf466d13bc90c2","tid":2444204,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"40f7368174ea6ebc94bbd328f4f1a7fe10f12f66","tid":2444204,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"點樣好法？"},{"pid":"961c3cbcc0a220544a9a6911eb57aafa7e27926c","tid":2444204,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f7368174ea6ebc94bbd328f4f1a7fe10f12f66","tid":2444204,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"點樣好法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"世上牛柳眾多，肥環燕瘦，無一有龍門那樣獨特的氣質。孤傲、無畏、自信、有著一股不羈的野性，她是最璀璨的光華結晶，如同一團烈火，激烈且張狂地燃燒著。她讓美味不再只是味覺上，而是由心真正的散發出來，她緊抓著眾人的眼和味蕾。再加之， 一絲嫩紅的肌紅蛋白（血水）所襯托出的空靈氣質，與在陽光照射下而形成的淡淡光暈，更若天女下凡，絕美無雙!"},{"pid":"7bc3c97f406935d84b9a5a60e397cf59be80422a","tid":2444204,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"請得起咁多打手仲唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955aa42be1d2cb8d9a8e5448976f7d6e8b12db56","tid":2444204,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc3c97f406935d84b9a5a60e397cf59be80422a","tid":2444204,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"請得起咁多打手仲唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"張假條（jj）唔做呢啲嘢"}]}